Text: I know most people won't care, but I forgot to mention that these books are not under copyright of any kind. They can be DL'd and UP'd without worry, share away.

Please be patient while downloading, my up-rate is about 150kbs. To limit time spent downloading and speed up the process I have enacted a bandwith queue. This means wait you turn and hope for seeders upon completion. I will get to you! I run 24/7. Thanks again.
Indeed it is, it's the entire collection from Toronto University's Robarts Library
